snippet.title: Bearly Delivered  - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Bearly Delivered is our upcoming 3D package adventure game! Roam your town as a delivery bear, throwing packages out of your van or placing them by hand. 

Follow us at:
https://bigseatstudios.com/
Discord: https://discord.gg/yX5XguFgN3
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@bigseatstudios
Twitter: https://twitter.com/bigseatstudios
